title: My Website
text:
My name is Lauren and I am 22 years old.
I am currently a student in Baruch’s MS Business Analytics Program.

My Dogs!
I have two dogs! Their names are:

Macaroni

Macaroni (Mack) is technically my brother’s dog, but we babysit him while he’s at work.
He is a Golden Retreiver and is 2 years old!


Rusty

Rusty is extremely loving and the smartest dog I have ever met.
He is a Pitbull/Lab mix and is 13 years old (we think, he’s a rescue)!
